{"tid":1647243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非行動整合平台","createTime":"2019-10-11T16:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T14:29:39.000Z","uid":52152,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7019c58b3753c4ed9388f0df9b67cf30fc93a6a1","tid":1647243,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:14:03.000Z","msg":"之前有post都討論過依家和理非既行動有以下既問題：<br />\n<ins>1) 行動太多，太亂</ins><br />\n同一日可以有唔同既行動，有啲撞時間，有啲就唔知有咩用，有啲就地點差太遠，太散，有時會成版都係行動post，基本上聚唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聚唔到人首先會俾外國人覺得個運動已經停止左，另外一次少人可能會令到下一次更加少人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins>2) 文宣嚴重不足</ins><br />\n有好多行動都係2日前，甚至即日係連登出post。有好多人包括我基本上唔知道有，有幾次都係啱啱行過即刻join<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位搞手巴絲要知道其實好多人係冇睇連登，初期有好多行動都係靠連儂痴文宣/airdrop 去spread開。如果要搞既話，起碼文宣都要預返最少2日左右，方便聚人<br />\n<br />\n以上兩個問題都可能係因為依家係冇一個平台去俾搞手們去夾時間，大家靠睇連登post入面討論又會好散，所以我開左一個TG group 同TG channel：<br />\n<br />\n和理非行動整合channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/woleifeiaction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwoleifeiaction&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=6f4c4562\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/woleifeiaction</a><br />\n<br />\n主要功能：<br />\n1) 發佈搞手們係group入面討論完既行動<br />\n2) 如果撞日子又夾唔到既時候，希望可以做埋投票既功能。盡可能將和理非既力量聚埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n和理非行動搞手討論group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/woleifeidiscuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwoleifeidiscuss&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=8e9ad27d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/woleifeidiscuss</a><br />\n<br />\n主要功能：<br />\n1) 俾搞手們去傾/討論黎緊既行動<br />\n2) 希望有埋文宣手足可以加入傾文宣設計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望做到個流程係：<br />\nTG group 搞手們傾/夾完 &gt; TG channel發佈 &gt; 連登/連儂/airdrop/落街推文宣 <br />\n<br />\n依個平台唔包括任何裝修裝飾快閃行動，因為狗仔一定會入黎mon post。所以以上既行動都係靠各位裝修師傅私下交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原諒樓主一把年紀唔太識用TG，如果巴絲覺得有咩可以改善既就提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0747265762b67a5b8f994c03ae7c8590f9177b1b","tid":1647243,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n<br />\n突發！香城online現已公開發售！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb03cf77b6a0dbe40044286a9b2497dcfe629e04","tid":1647243,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"希望有人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01d0125a0294ec8d65625d4112dcd1c46f788a1","tid":1647243,"uid":52152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e55f07f90314f10fb6a0db1695c801ad7d8a70","tid":1647243,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebca94b0d3f9e7ff1aacd8712a775860c0d5278","tid":1647243,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:17:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n需要個平台比所有和理非搞手傾<br />\n文宣組參考左先整日程"},{"pid":"088e97ab457f2118209a69c246d0fcf7e0aa2714","tid":1647243,"uid":138427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13de960a32d898e991b215c32f84652f6d39e8bc","tid":1647243,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:01:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebc2a5e9c78188279d2b2b3ffa6808c140818f1a","tid":1647243,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:03:19.000Z","msg":"P 牌一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45731a7504998c3dcc